author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at a supply chain attack, or two rather when it comes to the most popular software repository known as NPM. This happened in a way that many people think they're often to smart to fall for and today proves that's never really the case. Thanks for watching!

title: The Worst Cyberattack of 2025 Just Happened...
